               stealing a linen handkerchief, value 10 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17770910-54-victim457" type="victimName">
                     William
                      Lawrence
                  <interp inst="t17770910-54-victim457" type="surname" value="Lawrence"></interp>
